E4Plus1.uk.description: A Goldberg Thanksgiving: Beverly challenges Erica to participate in Jazzercise after Erica says her mum's obsession is sad. Marvin visits the family at Thanksgiving. (S2 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Locomotive Manipulation: Love is in the air when Amy convinces Sheldon to join her for a romantic train trip to Napa Valley to celebrate Valentine's Day. (S7 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Two-Timing Goldbergs: Love and loyalty win when Lainey comes home, and Adam and Carmen come to a crossroads in their relationship. (S10 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Crush: Beverly struggles with her feelings for a new crush, while Barry leases his own apartment without considering Joanne. (S10 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Better Annie: Adam's excited about introducing Carmen to his family, until he's shocked by a former incident between her and one of his siblings. (S10 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Flyer's Path to Victory: When the Flyers make it to the Stanley Cup finals, Barry implements superstitious protocols that the family must follow. (S10 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Handlebar: Gordon Ramsay takes on a time warp at the Handlebar restaurant and lounge in Mount Sinai, New York, where the owners are stuck in the 80s with an unenthusiastic chef. (S2 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sabatiello's: Gordon Ramsay sets his sights on Sabatiello's, an Italian restaurant in Connecticut that's better known for its owner Sammy's tantrums than the food. (S2 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Trobiano's: Gordon Ramsay meets struggling executive chef Anthony Trobiano, who's sinking under half a million dollars of debt at his restaurant in Great Neck, New York. (S2 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Jack's Waterfront: In Michigan, Gordon Ramsay visits a lakeside restaurant in a summer hotspot, where the food fails to match the fantastic views. Can Gordon turn the tide? (S2 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Proposal Proposal: Amy must decide whether or not to marry Sheldon and gives him an answer to his proposal. Howard and Bernadette struggle with some unexpected news. (S11 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Retraction Reaction: Leonard angers the university during an embarrassing interview. Amy and Bernadette must hide their success from Sheldon and Howard. (S11 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Relaxation Integration: Amy tries to convince Sheldon that he has a more laid-back side. Raj and Stuart compete to woo Bernadette's new colleague Ruchi. (S11 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Explosion Implosion: Howard and Sheldon bond on a trip to the desert to launch a model rocket. Leonard is annoyed when his mother befriends Penny. (S11 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Kid Who Would Be King
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2019) Fantasy adventure. A 12-year-old from modern-day suburbia finds King Arthur's sword Excalibur and must save the country from a sinister sorceress. With Patrick Stewart.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Take My Wife, Sleaze: Homer wins a motorbike and forms the Hell's Satans biker gang with Lenny, Carl, Moe and Flanders. But then they run into the original Hell's Satans... (S11 Ep8/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Little Big Mom: When Marge breaks her leg in a skiing accident, Lisa takes over running the Simpson household, and Homer and Bart end up moving to a leper colony in Hawaii. (S11 Ep10/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Skinner's Sense of Snow: When a huge snowdrift engulfs the school, Bart leads the kids in a rebellion, gagging Principal Skinner and tying him to a chair as they run amok. (S12 Ep8/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homr: When Homer loses all the family's money with an unwise investment, he becomes a human guinea pig to earn some cash - and that's when he becomes extremely intelligent... (S12 Ep9/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pokey Mom: Marge notices a prison inmate's artistic talent and helps him to get a job painting a mural at the school. But he clashes with Skinner. Michael Keaton guest stars. (S12 Ep10/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Worst Episode Ever: Bart and Milhouse end up running Comic Book Guy's shop after he has a heart attack. And, while he recovers, Comic Book Guy falls in love... (S12 Ep11/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Tennis the Menace: Homer builds a tennis court in the back garden but becomes jealous of Bart's tennis skills and swears revenge at the Krusty Klassic tournament. (S12 Ep12/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great Christmas Bake Off
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sandi, Noel, Paul and Prue are joined by Liam and Flo from the 2017 Bake Off, and Jane and Andrew from 2016's show. Plus The Darkness perform Christmas Time (Don't Let the Bells End).

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox Festive Special
E4Plus1.uk.description: The armchair critics take aim at Christmas TV, including Gavin and Stacey, Strictly Come Dancing, Home Alone, Dracula, and Jamie's Easy Christmas Countdown.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: This time on the 'Box: The Inheritance, You Bet! On Tour, KPopped, Emmerdale, The Guest, 90 Day Fianc UK, This Morning (roast dinner) and ITV News (Angela Rayner). (S26 Ep2) [SL]

Film4.uk.title: The Unbearable Weight of...
Film4.uk.description: ...Massive Talent: (2022) Nicolas Cage stars as, er, Nic Cage - an unbearably talented actor caught up in a CIA investigation while trying to resurrect his ailing career. With Pedro Pascal.

Film4.uk.title: Memory
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Action with Liam Neeson as a septuagenarian hitman; Monica Bellucci as a villain who hires hitmen to hit him, and Guy Pearce as an FBI agent investigating it all.

Film4.uk.title: The Real Charlie Chaplin
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Documentary. Who was Charlie Chaplin? A simple enough question on the surface of it. But dig a bit deeper and separating the man from the character he played is a little trickier...

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Father Brown
Film4.uk.description: (1954) Crime-comedy starring Alec Guinness. A priest is tasked with accompanying a priceless religious artifact from London to Rome. But the prolific thief Flambeau is hot on his trail...

Film4.uk.title: Saraband for Dead Lovers
Film4.uk.description: (1948) Historical drama starring Joan Greenwood and Stewart Granger. Princess Dorothea marries the future king of England. But then she meets a Swedish count...

Film4.uk.title: Nicholas Nickleby
Film4.uk.description: (1947) Drama with Derek Bond, based on Charles Dickens' novel. After his father dies, Nicholas seeks the help of his cold, avaricious, scheming uncle. Predictably, it doesn't go well.

Film4.uk.title: The Colditz Story
Film4.uk.description: (1954) Classic Second World War drama. John Mills, Lionel Jeffries and Bryan Forbes star as just some of the POWs determined to break out of the infamous German 'escape-proof' prison.

Film4.uk.title: Fisherman's Friends
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Heart-warming comedy based on the real-life story of the Cornish folk ensemble who took the UK charts by storm in 2010, starring Daniel Mays and Tuppence Middleton.

Film4.uk.title: Boston Strangler
Film4.uk.description: (2023) Keira Knightley stars as Loretta McLaughlin, the reporter who fought 60s chauvinism to break the story of the notorious titular serial killer, in Matt Ruskin's true crime procedural.

Film4.uk.title: She Said
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Fact-based drama with Zoe Kazan and Carey Mulligan. New York Times journalists Jodi Kantor and Megan Twohey investigate the sexual abuses of Hollywood producer Harvey Weinstein.

Film4.uk.title: French Exit
Film4.uk.description: (2020) Comedy drama with Michelle Pfeiffer. A skint Manhattan socialite moves to Paris with her son and a cat... which may or may not contain the spirit of her dead husband.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: The Sound Barrier
Film4.uk.description: (1952) Drama starring Ralph Richardson as a pioneering aviator determined to break the sound barrier, even if it means risking the lives of those closest to him. Directed by David Lean.

Film4.uk.title: Gideon of Scotland Yard
Film4.uk.description: (1958) Drama. Jack Hawkins stars as Police Inspector Gideon, who faces outrage and danger in his quest to bring London's criminals to justice. With Anna Massey, John Loder and Cyril Cusack.

Film4.uk.title: Animal Farm
Film4.uk.description: (1954) George Orwell's cautionary tale reimagined in cartoon form. A farm's animals revolt against their abusive owner only for the pigs to become drunk with their newly found power.

Film4.uk.title: Footsteps in the Fog
Film4.uk.description: (1955) Atmospheric Victorian melodrama. Stewart Granger plays a sinister aristocrat who poisons his wife. However, his maid (Jean Simmons) knows his secret and tries to use it against him.

Film4.uk.title: Legends of the Fall
Film4.uk.description: (1994) Oscar-winning turn-of-the-century drama with Brad Pitt and Anthony Hopkins. A Montana patriarch's son falls for his brother's fiance, setting off a tragic chain of events.

Film4.uk.title: American Gangster Special
Film4.uk.description: Denzel Washington, Russell Crowe and director Ridley Scott talk about making American Gangster, the 2007 crime epic based on an unlikely true story.

Film4.uk.title: American Gangster
Film4.uk.description: (2007) True crime thriller directed by Ridley Scott. An outcast New York cop (Russell Crowe) is charged with bringing down entrepreneurial Harlem drug lord Frank Lucas (Denzel Washington).

Film4.uk.title: The Mechanic
Film4.uk.description: (2011) Thriller with Jason Statham and Donald Sutherland. A hitman is ordered to kill his mentor, but then takes on the dead man's son as an apprentice. Could get complicated... and deadly.

Film4.uk.title: A Quiet Place Part II
Film4.uk.description: (2020) Hushed-horror sequel with Emily Blunt and Cillian Murphy. Armed only with a hearing aid, can the family evade the vicious aliens with super-hearing, and find a community to live in?

Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Wonder Park
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Animated adventure featuring the voices of Jennifer Garner, Mila Kunis, John Oliver and Matthew Broderick. A girl's imaginary theme park comes to life when her mum goes to hospital.

Film4.uk.title: Spies in Disguise
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Animated spy comedy caper with the voice of Will Smith. The 'world's most awesome spy' gets framed and has to go undercover as a pigeon to prove his innocence.

Film4.uk.title: The Desert Fox
Film4.uk.description: (1951) Drama. James Mason stars in Henry Hathaway's sympathetic portrait of Field Marshal Erwin Rommel in the final years of his life during the Second World War. With Jessica Tandy.

Film4.uk.title: The Perfect Catch
Film4.uk.description: (2005) Comedy. Ben (Jimmy Fallon) must choose between his two loves: Lindsey (Drew Barrymore) and the Boston Red Sox baseball team. Based on Nick Hornby's novel Fever Pitch.

Film4.uk.title: The Day After Tomorrow
Film4.uk.description: (2004) Tense sci-fi thriller starring Jake Gyllenhaal and Dennis Quaid. A scientist sets out to save his son when global warming plunges the world into a sudden climatic catastrophe.

Film4.uk.title: The King's Man
Film4.uk.description: (2021) The spy-caper franchise continues with the origins story of the Kingsman agency, as a plucky group battle an international conspiracy at the outbreak of WWI. With Ralph Fiennes.

Film4.uk.title: Scream
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Meta-comedy horror 're-quel' with Courteney Cox. Killer Ghostface returns to shock the younger generation out of their love of 'elevated horror' with a bit of old-fashioned slashing.

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Fred Dibnah's Made in Britain
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: The Engineering Workshop: Fred Dibnah and his team are in the mountains of Snowdonia to visit the Welsh Slate Museum on the final stage of their journey. Ep11

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Fred Dibnah's Made in Britain
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: A Lifetime's Achievement: The concluding part of the enlightening series on engineering. In this final episode, Fred Dibnah travels down to London to collect his MBE from the Queen. Ep12

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: The Fred Dibnah Story
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Beginnings: The life of the Bolton steeplejack, explaining how his TV career began. This episode sees him working on the spectacular demolition that would set him on the road to fame. Ep1

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Moskvitch: Dave's drawn to a Fiat Uno 45 in '1970's beige', with 36,000 miles on the clock. S9 Ep11

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Canal Boat Diaries
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Windsor to Godalming: While exploring the Wey and Godalming Navigations, Robbie gets caught in a storm and falls off his narrowboat. He also uncovers rock history in Guildford. S6 Ep5

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Guy Martin: Proper Jobs
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Mountain Rescue Dog Handler: Guy loves dogs - he therefore jumps at the opportunity to become part of a dog mountain rescue team tackling dangerous terrain as a mountain rescue guide. S1 Ep4

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: How Britain Worked
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Guy Martin and a team from the Black Country Living Museum restore a Newcomen engine, an 18th-century steam-powered device used principally to pump water out of mines. S1 Ep4

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: 1961 Morris Minor 1000: Paul and Jack head to Staffordshire to pick up five vehicles from collector Rob's colossal barn, including a Mini and a Morris Minor. S8 Ep3
